{"featured_counts":1,"common_counts":37,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/562357157/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=5\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/562357157/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=3\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":12},"data":[{"id":567569113,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567569113","content":"“日心说发现之前，所有人都觉得你是一个肉体凡胎，都不可能跑遍地球，又怎么能断言地球面积是有限的。你看，这不跟评论里一堆自以为是的人一样么，什么高中生证明哥猜就是普通人跑赢博尔特，就是单挑把贝克汉姆踢个20比0的难度都出来。而实际上呢，日心说就摆在那里，简单明了，静静地等着有缘人发现他。他被发现了以后，就是简单的连一个小学生都可以理解。而被发现之前，丈量地球面积就是被无数人视为不可能，太难了。”\u003cbr\u003e这段太搞笑了。日心说跟丈量地球面积有啥关系。。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546102907,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","url_token":"huang-yu-zhu-38-10","name":"黄毓宁","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","user_type":"people","headline":"水货大学生/期待为科学奋斗/LGBT","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":2,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":4,"child_comments":[{"id":567610309,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567610309","content":"日心说发现之前，大家认为地球是平的无限的。另外你要的例子我给你举例一个最简单的，青霉素。几千年来这么多中医西医无数的努力，都拿细菌毫无办法。甚者认为及其困难的手术可以治疗一些疾那么一些更严重的疾病(当初还没有细菌的概念，只发现症状严重)，可能要更高超的医术才行，甚至认为是上帝对人类的惩罚，这不跟现在很多人觉得哥猜难到只有上帝才会证明一样么。然而就是一个普通的医生，无意中发现了青霉素，然后一切都有了改变。青霉素的提取很难吗？一点也不难，被发现后简单到当时的技术立刻可以量产。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546127514,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","url_token":"xie-qiu-chen-99","name":"小小晓芾","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","user_type":"people","headline":"精通城市规划，房地产发展","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","url_token":"huang-yu-zhu-38-10","name":"黄毓宁","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","user_type":"people","headline":"水货大学生/期待为科学奋斗/LGBT","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":567619819,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567619819","content":"不好意思，地心说时代人们已经认为地球是球体了。地心说的图景是：月亮、太阳、当时的五大行星和恒星天一起围绕地球转动，并且当时人们认为这个天球，也就是宇宙本身，是很小的。平的无限的东西怎么成为一个有限球体的中心？\u003cbr\u003e您举了一个实验科学的例子。实验科学本身就是一个试错过程，是有很大偶然性的，在科学历史中也有很多由于偶然发现一样东西的例子，但是在数学上并非如此。\u003cbr\u003e再者说，细菌于1673年才被发现，而在19世纪人们才开始认为细菌可能导致疾病，所谓“中医西医几千年无数的努力”属于无稽之谈。人们发现细菌可能导致疾病，到青霉素被发现，中间只隔了不到一百年的时间，这还是在当年那么差的实验条件下。再者说，在显微镜下能观察到细菌破损是发现青霉素的必要条件，而显微镜的发明是17世纪的事情。也就是说，17世纪以前的人们，无论怎么努力，也都既无法发现细菌也无法发现青霉素。另外，青霉素从发现到量产一共花了25年的时间。\u003cbr\u003e换句话来说，青霉素的例子不是“我怎么没‘想’到”，而是“我怎么没‘做’到”，而且这个没做到还是17世纪之后的，之前是根本做不到。\u003cbr\u003e而数学并非如此，并没有什么生产力的条件来限制数学家的思维。用科学路上的一个偶然来臆测花了三百年、从9+9推进到1+2，凝聚前人无数智慧结晶的一座山峰，真是太肤浅了。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546130442,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","url_token":"huang-yu-zhu-38-10","name":"黄毓宁","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","user_type":"people","headline":"水货大学生/期待为科学奋斗/LGBT","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","url_token":"xie-qiu-chen-99","name":"小小晓芾","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","user_type":"people","headline":"精通城市规划，房地产发展","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0}]}]}
